data.description: Wouldn't it be nice to have a house where you don't have to worry about the plumbing, HVAC, roof, or electricity? This home was built in 2010 so all of your systems are relatively new! Maintaining your beautiful home is easier with vinyl siding and laminate flooring.  1126 sq. ft affords you plenty of space for a comfortable lifestyle!  The awesome back deck extends your living space to the outdoors.  Plenty of room for barbecues and entertainment. The backyard has plenty of room for recreation, and outdoor games, not to mention the garden you have wanted to make! Another fantastic feature is the location, two blocks off main street, means easy access to downtown shopping, downtown dining, cultural events and festivals. Priced just over $200 a square foot this house packs all of features for the money.  This home is eligible for 100% financing, USDA, FHA, VA, and conventional.
